summary: This is a photo sheet and incident report from the Metropolitan Correctional Center in New York documenting a possible suicide attempt by inmate Jeffrey Epstein on July 23, 2019, at 1:27 AM. The report includes details about the location and time of the incident and subsequent photograph.

persons.name: Jeffrey Epstein
persons.context: Listed as the inmate involved in a possible suicide attempt at the Metropolitan Correctional Center on July 23, 2019.

events.title: Possible Suicide Attempt by Jeffrey Epstein

locations: Metropolitan Correctional Center, New York, N.Y.
keyFacts: Jeffrey Epstein was involved in a possible suicide attempt on July 23, 2019, at 1:27 AM.
The incident occurred in the Special Housing Unit (SHU) of the Metropolitan Correctional Center in New York.
Photographs of the incident were taken by a Lieutenant at 1:55 AM on the same date.
